            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p>
                    <lb/>Τόδε μνεμεῖον Ζακκαρίας <expan><abbr>μάρ</abbr><ex>τυρος</ex></expan>
                    
                    <lb/><expan><abbr>πρεσβητ</abbr><ex>έρου</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>θεοσεβε</abbr><ex>στάτου</ex></expan> παππέας <expan><abbr>Ἰοά</abbr><ex>ννου</ex></expan>.
                    
                    
                    
                    <lb/><g ref="cross">+</g> Ἡ ψυχή.
                    
                    
                    
                    <lb/>Ὁ θάφος Συμεὼν ὃς ἦν
                    
                    <lb/>δικα<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>ότατος <expan><abbr>ἄνθρωπ</abbr><ex>ος</ex></expan>
                    
                    <lb/>καὶ γέρ<supplied reason="lost">ω</supplied>ν εὐσηβήστατος
                    
                    <lb/>καὶ παράκλησιν
                    
                    <lb/>λαοῦ
                    
                    <lb/><expan><abbr>προσδεχ</abbr><ex>όμενος</ex></expan>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>This is the tomb of Zechariah, martyr, most pious priest, father of John.
                    
                    The soul.
                    
                    Tomb of Symeon who was a most righteous man and a most pious elder and who awaited the consolation for the people (of Israel).</p>
            </div>
